{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And those who were going to come their voluntarily, at least in the early stages, they were even going to have some food given to them, I think three kilos of bread and a kilo of marmalade, something like that.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there were a number of people who went there who were hungry, and who went voluntarily.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those posters appeared on the 22nd, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the same day, or the day before I'm not sure, [GERMAN], who was the head of the [GERMAN], committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when [GERMAN] committed suicide, everybody knew that it was-- the whole thing was very bad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [GERMAN] committed suicide because he was forced, he was told, to sign those notices.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he refused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He refused.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the end, he didn't sign.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But he committed suicide straight after.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was possibly a mistake that he didn't speak openly to the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that was-- but, anyway, he showed a great amount of courage by committing suicide as well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we, we must have already been warned greatly the day, or two, or three days before, because before the posters appeared, already on the day before, on the 21st I think, we went to the shop.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, what does it mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's the shop, as I said, where factories which were working for the British-- working for the German army, or for the German industry.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were quite a number of them in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To But the real big ones were [POLISH], and [POLISH], and there were some [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were some others.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were probably quite a number of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, my uncles, brothers of my mother [POLISH], they all-- those are nicknames, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's how I always knew them.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
